Kynurenine Pathway

ggplot(Kynurenine, aes(x = analysis, y = Kynurenine_mean, fill = analysis)) + geom_boxplot() + xlab("Group") + ylab("Kynurenine Activation") + ggtitle("Kynurenine Activation") + scale_x_discrete(limits=c("naive", "grouped_pr", "grouped_pd")) + theme(legend.position = "none") + geom_signif(comparisons = list(c("grouped_pd", "grouped_pr")), map_signif_level=TRUE, y_position = 3.5) + 
  geom_signif(comparisons = list(c("grouped_pd", "naive")), map_signif_level=TRUE, y_position = 4) + 
  geom_signif(comparisons = list(c("grouped_pr", "naive")), map_signif_level=TRUE, y_position = 2) +  scale_x_discrete(limits=c("naive", "grouped_pr", "grouped_pd")) + theme(legend.position = "none")
